{"tid":918560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【基因改造嬰】涉事醫院稱無負責接生：不認識賀建奎　質疑有人造假已報警","createTime":"2018-11-27T10:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T12:17:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c93f3b48d15407fa851e804c235b728644d480b3","tid":918560,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181127/s00004/4b523658ddff0c0c42ca8b72e3e783e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181127%2Fs00004%2F4b523658ddff0c0c42ca8b72e3e783e0.jpg&h=e5de8657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳南方科技大學副教授賀建奎昨宣布，一對名為露露和娜娜的經基因編輯、對愛滋病免疫的女嬰本月在內地健康誕生，消息一出學術界嘩然，引發倫理爭議。然而，內地媒體「經濟觀察網」今日刊登一篇訪問誕生女嬰的涉事醫院「深圳和美婦兒科醫院」總經理程珍的報道，對方指根本不認識賀建奎，更懷疑有人在事件中造假，已報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n據早前流傳的文件所示，該宗實驗由包括上述醫院領導黃華鋒在內的7人簽字同意下開展。然而院方今日卻表示該院根本沒醫生簽過相關文件，亦從未進行有關實驗，更沒有任何基因改造嬰兒誕生。<br />\n<br />\n「經濟觀察網」記者亦親身前往涉事醫院，打算訪問文件中提及的「黃華鋒醫生」，院方卻表示上班期間不便接受採訪；記者又打算前往醫院辦公室採訪院方領導，惟很快被保安勸退；另外，記者在醫院公開的醫生資料欄上，僅找到文件中聲稱曾有份簽字的「婦產科主任鄧興書」一人，而其餘6人資料則未見蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181127/s00004/1543308268747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181127%2Fs00004%2F1543308268747&d=sUJnQeXCEQ186RwnaT2I3b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d90c71c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181127%2Fs00004%2F1543308268747&h=de3d72e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181127/s00004/1543308268747</a>"},{"pid":"0a6dce757c4d8c7b9c5f382a107ff88b5562ba8a","tid":918560,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"嗰兩個BB女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48129b862e9dfd1a0dfdfade4fc32115eedd2f46","tid":918560,"uid":46277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"都估到係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d03d61a1008184f61af93e92f61b3cda92bbfc","tid":918560,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"急急割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2790032da0c3f0f8b7fd10ef769078ad94372a23","tid":918560,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02d03d61a1008184f61af93e92f61b3cda92bbfc","tid":918560,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"急急割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"條友好似話今日黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cee58a4141ac0ce0ce31588669bdb49c112129","tid":918560,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"信係真果班驗下腦啦<br />\n<br />\n支那狗最鐘意認屎認屁"},{"pid":"656368073f130d615462a9a9145557bec4721a3b","tid":918560,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎大陸想秘密做d野"},{"pid":"07adcb6eea08e3539a1ea78626fd166dd37e1b08","tid":918560,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"本來係想威威<br />\n點知畀全世界圍插<br />\n扮係中國最聞名嘅假嘢嚟蒙混過關"}]}